This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with background modeling in high-resolution video processing. The paper also mentions the use of singular value decomposition, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The compressed sensing and matrix sketching techniques used in the cDMD algorithm are also relevant to data science (cs.DS) and signal processing (cs.SI).
